Other Special Occasion Flowers

Flowers from any special occasion can be pressed, preserved and framed so they can be displayed in your home as a cherished keepsake.  Special occasions may include:  Mothers Day, Valentine’s Day, Graduation, Anniversary, Birthday, Prom or “Just because you Care”.  

Contact B’s Garden Treasures at info@BGTreasures.com or 315-789-2911 for pricing.  

